{"tid":1901732,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"拒用替身代出席公開場合   普京：我是真的","createTime":"2020-02-28T03:51:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-28T04:02:44.000Z","uid":184679,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"45331f10f93af291ed65bdd8bcbab67e11b467a7","tid":1901732,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T03:51:46.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯總統普京周四（27日）承認，政府曾有秘密計劃安排替身代他出席公開場合，惟被他否決，並堅稱他是真的普京。<br />\n<br />\n國營傳媒塔斯社（TASS）列出連串俄羅斯網民熱門搜索結果，其中包括「普京替身」。普京周四受訪時披露，從未用過替身，但承認政府內部曾討論過，「我拒絕用替身。當時正值對抗恐怖主義最艱難時期」。1999至2000年，俄羅斯對車臣分離分子發動第二次戰爭，普京由總理變總統負責督戰，俄軍獲勝後，車臣分離分子經常在俄國大城市發動自殺式炸彈襲擊。普京承認，2000年代初有人建議他用替身，以減低公開露面的風險，惟該計劃遭他否決。<br />\n<br />\n（法新社）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/article/20200227/s00005/1582812099477/%E6%99%AE%E4%BA%AC-%E6%8B%92%E7%B5%95%E6%9B%BF%E8%BA%AB%E4%BB%A3%E5%87%BA%E5%B8%AD%E5%85%AC%E9%96%8B%E5%A0%B4%E5%90%88\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2Farticle%2F20200227%2Fs00005%2F1582812099477%2F%25E6%2599%25AE%25E4%25BA%25AC-%25E6%258B%2592%25E7%25B5%2595%25E6%259B%25BF%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E5%2587%25BA%25E5%25B8%25AD%25E5%2585%25AC%25E9%2596%258B%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E5%2590%2588&d=d7tjXuyQMlDyBW65i2Gj0QKEBJewdHKi9Ib5gSSGE6s%3D&h=67ce7e17\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2Farticle%2F20200227%2Fs00005%2F1582812099477%2F%25E6%2599%25AE%25E4%25BA%25AC-%25E6%258B%2592%25E7%25B5%2595%25E6%259B%25BF%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E5%2587%25BA%25E5%25B8%25AD%25E5%2585%25AC%25E9%2596%258B%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E5%2590%2588&h=59aaaaa3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/article/20200227/s00005/1582812099477/%E6%99%AE%E4%BA%AC-%E6%8B%92%E7%B5%95%E6%9B%BF%E8%BA%AB%E4%BB%A3%E5%87%BA%E5%B8%AD%E5%85%AC%E9%96%8B%E5%A0%B4%E5%90%88</a>"},{"pid":"00020ca1f1cb13718878362b947d7ae24033d00e","tid":190173